When i started this map i was without any ideas and i came to fpsbana maps section and i find paintball sub category and i though thats it so here it is hope you like and watch the head ;D

1 Open the 'Steam' folder
2 Then 'steammaps'.
3 Now open the folder with your Steam username.
4 and next 'counterstrike source' or 'counterstrike source beta' folder. 
5 The open the 'cstrike' folder then 'maps'.
6 Extract the bsp file.
7 copy the bsp file.
8 Paste it on the 'maps' folder.
9 Launch the game.
10 ENJOY!


This map is for free use on any server as long as you agree to:
-Not decompile this map!
-Not remove any logos placed in this map!
